name: Pinel Panic
description:
Scoring game made at WonderJam 2020 by team Cabayajeti.

The theme was "Frenzy" and we had arcade and dialog constraints.

Your goal is to satisfy the highest number of patients in the hospital.

Made by:

  • BABU Baptiste
  • CORSINI Timothée
  • FARINES Jean
